wn.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你估銀行鐘意用乜AUTHENTICATION都得架？<br />\nHKMA 都有指引，下年要強制2FA 先做到INTERNET BANKING 呀 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkma.gov.hk/eng/key-functions/banking-stability/internet-banking/two-factor-authentication.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkma.gov.hk%2Feng%2Fkey-functions%2Fbanking-stability%2Finternet-banking%2Ftwo-factor-authentication.shtml&d=TATvGuIp7QFs3xzS4bhhzttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=686f0412\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkma.gov.hk/eng/key-functions/banking-stability/internet-banking/two-factor-authentication.shtml</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n關咩事， FaceID 同touchID 都係 Biometric Authentication<br />\n如果FaceID 唔符合 HKMA 指引， touchID 咪一樣唔得</blockquote><br />\n我覺得兩件事，ma應該唔會tech到咁先既<br />\n我估 biometric 對ma 哩d科技盲黎講得fingerprint<br />\n依家多左face 遲下有eyeball，voice咁<br />\n依家MA未出聲，就試下得邊間d老細淆底囉"},{"pid":"9426cdc474e7665deefd60631bb930bd0d6024ce","tid":473680,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:28:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>評分幾低都無人理啦<br />\n打上cs投訴，仲要迫佢地覆原因同幾時有得用<br />\n總之就迫佢地d人去做野就得架啦</blockquote><br />\n已正評你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽朝去做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS有人負評你 係咪痕身IT狗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41301114cb90d2a3f8574b062c1f372bd5c04787","tid":473680,"uid":25266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:30:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成班友唔識野亂咁吹。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你估銀行鐘意用乜AUTHENTICATION都得架？<br />\nHKMA 都有指引，下年要強制2FA 先做到INTERNET BANKING 呀 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkma.gov.hk/eng/key-functions/banking-stability/internet-banking/two-factor-authentication.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkma.gov.hk%2Feng%2Fkey-functions%2Fbanking-stability%2Finternet-banking%2Ftwo-factor-authentication.sht